  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Employees can use the clock in/out feature to accurately record their work hours, enabling managers to monitor hours worked during pay periods, track absenteeism, and maintain precise profitability reports. Staff members with the &quot;Timesheet Required&quot; option enabled in their Staff Profile can clock in/out directly within RepairQ. Employees can clock in/out from any open terminal without logging in under their profile.</p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Administrators can customize the required credentials for clocking in/out. For details, refer to our article, <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2024734723\" rel=\"nofollow\">Staff Management Settings</a>.</p><h3 id=\"GettingStarted:ClockIn/OutofRepairQ-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934524447\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maintaining an Accurate Profitability Report</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1929379890/Staff+Management+Add+and+Deactivate+Staff+Profiles\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1929379890\" data-linked-resource-version=\"27\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Add and Deactivate Staff Profiles</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1928921099\" rel=\"nofollow\">Getting Started: Login, Password Reset, and User Profile Customization</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2028634130\" rel=\"nofollow\">Switch Between Staff Profiles Without Logging Out of RepairQ</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/2024734723/Staff+Management+Settings\" data-linked-resource-id=\"2024734723\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Staff Management Settings</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1928986634/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"GettingStarted:ClockIn/OutofRepairQ-ClockingIn(StartingtheTimecard)\">Clocking In (Starting the Timecard)</h2><p>On the top Navigation Bar, click the <strong>Location Dropdown</strong>. From the list of selections, click <strong>Clock In/Out</strong>. A Time Clock pop-up will appear. Enter your Username and/or PIN/Password and click <strong>Go</strong>.</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: Admins can update authentication username/pin requirements for clocking in/out in <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/2024734723/Staff+Management+Settings\" data-linked-resource-id=\"2024734723\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Staff Management Settings</a>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"442\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1928986634/Clock%201.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" alt=\"Clock In 2.png\" width=\"452\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1928986634/Clock%20In%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>The pop-up will show your current Time Clock Status and the total hours for today and the current week. Click <strong>Clock In</strong> to begin recording your time.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" alt=\"Clock In 3.png\" width=\"452\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1928986634/Clock%20In%203.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>You will be asked to confirm that you would like to clock in. Click <strong>Confirm</strong>, and you will be notified that your clock-in was successful and the time clock has started. You can also see your clock-in status on the dashboard under the <strong>Get Started</strong> section.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" alt=\"Clock In 4.png\" width=\"452\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1928986634/Clock%20In%204.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" alt=\"Clock In 5.png\" width=\"452\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1928986634/Clock%20In%205.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"GettingStarted:ClockIn/OutofRepairQ-ClockOut(StoptheTimecard)\">Clock Out (Stop the Timecard)</h2><p /><p>Navigate to <strong>Location Dropdown</strong> \u2192 <strong>Clock In/Out</strong> and enter your login PIN/Password. The pop-up will show your current Time Clock Status and the total logged hours for today and the current week. Click <strong>Clock Out </strong>to stop recording your time. You are asked to confirm that you would like to clock out. Click <strong>Confirm</strong>, and you will be notified that your clock-out was successful and the time clock has stopped.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" alt=\"Clock In 6.png\" width=\"507\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1928986634/Clock%20In%206.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" alt=\"Clock In 7.png\" width=\"507\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1928986634/Clock%20In%207.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.22.X</p>",
